---
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-9 gap-y-8 gap-x-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-4 md:col-span-3 justify-end">
        <div class="flex justify-center ">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 640 512" class="fill-bright-700" width="250">
